Hello, thank you for contacting Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Alexander Diaz. How can I assist you today?

I'm really upset! I've been trying to use my gift card, but it's not working, and I'm getting nowhere with this issue!

I'm sorry to hear that you're having trouble. Let me help resolve this for you. May I have your name, please?

It's Olivia Lewis.

Thank you, Olivia. Can you tell me the gift card number so I can check the details?

It's one, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, zero.

Thank you. And just to verify, could you also provide the email address associated with the gift card?

Sure, it's olivia.lewis@example.com.

Thank you, Olivia. I've checked our system, and it seems like there was a technical issue. I've reactivated your gift card, and it should work now. Please try using it again.

Alright, I'll do that. I appreciate your help, Alexander. Thank you.

You're welcome, Olivia. Thank you for your patience. If you need any more assistance, don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
